Following last year's Playland, Johnny Marr has announced a new solo live album. Adrenalin Baby, recorded primarily at Marr's Brixton Academy and Manchester Apollo shows during the 2014 Playland tour, comes out October 9 through Warners. Below, check out the tracklist, which includes a few Smiths numbers, Electronic's "Getting Away With It", and a cover of the  "I Fought the Law" (originally by the Crickets and popularized by the Clash)
